+# Digital Twin with SpiderMind Omega Integration
+
+This directory contains the Digital Twin implementation with SpiderMind Omega integration components. The integration enhances the Digital Twin's capabilities for understanding complex relationships, detecting knowledge gaps, making advanced predictions, and mapping consciousness topology.
+
+## Directory Structure
+
+- `adapters/`: SpiderMind Omega adapter implementations
+  - `entanglement_matrix.py`: EntanglementMatrix adapter for analyzing relationships
+  - `void_analyzer.py`: VoidAnalyzer adapter for detecting knowledge gaps
+  - `predictive_engine.py`: Enhanced PredictiveEngine adapter for advanced predictions
+  - `consciousness_mapper.py`: Enhanced ConsciousnessMapper adapter for mapping consciousness topology
+- `personality/`: Enhanced personality components
+  - `engine_enhanced.py`: Enhanced PersonalityEngine with SpiderMind Omega integration
+- `memory/`: Enhanced memory components
+  - `system_enhanced.py`: Enhanced MemorySystem with SpiderMind Omega integration
+- `conversation/`: Enhanced conversation components
+  - `engine_enhanced.py`: Enhanced ConversationEngine with SpiderMind Omega integration
+- `examples/`: Example scripts demonstrating the use of SpiderMind Omega adapters
+  - `spidermind_integration_example.py`: Example script demonstrating all adapters
+- `tests/`: Tests for SpiderMind Omega adapters and integration
